Class HangmanGUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • HangmanGUI

  • public final class HangmanGUI
extends Object
    Class HangmanGUI includes a static main method that reads a dictionary of words to be used during the game, then plays a game with the user via the console.
    Version:
    1.1
    Author:
    Dr. Jody Paul
